  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-0.1 (agent session creation), US-0.2 (context loading at start)
  5→ *
  6→ * Validates that the Brain MCP lifecycle hooks correctly start and end
  7→ * agent sessions. These hooks fire when an agent starts/stops a session,
  8→ * and they register the agent with Brain's knowledge graph context system.
  9→ *
 10→ * Driving ports: POST /api/mcp/:ws/sessions/start
 11→ *                POST /api/mcp/:ws/sessions/end
 12→ */
