  1→/**
  2→ * Review Flow: Diff Review, Accept, Reject with Feedback
  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-2.1 (review agent output), US-2.2 (accept),
  5→ *         US-2.3 (reject and provide feedback)
  6→ *
  7→ * Validates the complete review cycle: user views the diff and session
  8→ * summary, then either accepts the work (merging changes) or rejects it
  9→ * with feedback (agent resumes incorporating the feedback).
 10→ *
 11→ * Driving ports: GET  /api/orchestrator/:ws/sessions/:id/review
 12→ *                POST /api/orchestrator/:ws/sessions/:id/accept
 13→ *                POST /api/orchestrator/:ws/sessions/:id/reject
 14→ */
